{"tid":1537812,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［細思極恐］有冇人已經覺得畜龍 其實全部都係公安同武警","createTime":"2019-09-04T05:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T16:15:12.000Z","uid":293667,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"32b9ef7c3e70e2f7f6353b60eaffc3dd0604e20c","tid":1537812,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:12:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/20oxPHR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F20oxPHR.png&h=b09842d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我一早已經覺得係 雲海個fb更加出左個post講<br />\n我覺得呢件事基本上唔需要f唔fc<br />\n因為831打人個班就係畜龍 入哂車廂咁打法<br />\n佢地成班似係唔受控制 <br />\n仲要咁重手下下打頭 睇直播係唔小人爆頭<br />\n講緊既佢地全部係市民look 冇裝<br />\n我自己覺得香港人冷血極都有限啦<br />\n係大陸人先可能唔當我地係人咁打 <br />\n雖然我都覺得強姦單野要fc 無當時人出黎都唔信<br />\n但如果真係有大量大陸人落左黎佢地咁做都唔出奇<br />\n加上最近有唔小自殺案 疑點重重<br />\n831有畜龍唔小心打死人真係吾意外<br />\n前線要更加小心 特別係女義士<br />\n<br />\n成件事自己思考下可能性有幾大 <br />\n以上都係個人觀點 我唔係帶風同恐慌<br />\n<br />\n但香港人要團結係真 外國人幫唔到幾多<br />\n警察應該會越來越多人 直至成件事完"},{"pid":"2dc3a113fc0eeba25e6189f0763d65edc439ab7e","tid":1537812,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:12:27.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c1caa5383a0513af04e1ddaf0fdd88acd18a499","tid":1537812,"uid":31151,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:23:23.000Z","msg":"鄧竟成個仔咪速龍 同市民互屌得最多就係佢地 點會係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6788ea4b77a6f938761281447f6e1c98e19d306","tid":1537812,"uid":276758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:24:52.000Z","msg":"你知 我知 單眼佬都知<br />\n但係可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前細個返廣州,啲親戚講過<br />\n好多公安都係孤兒院出黎<br />\n一早比人洗哂腦加上無父無母<br />\n基本上點鬧點勸都係嘥氣<br />\n暴戾冇血性,賤命一條"},{"pid":"84e7be493460f1651a033fce4b7b8d121141c5fb","tid":1537812,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:44:18.000Z","msg":"同速蟲開拖吧！反正被捉到都死，不如拼死一博"},{"pid":"008be0ff33f0cec28134852e401a8727e862f38e","tid":1537812,"uid":262737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:46:16.000Z","msg":"又洗白<br />\n老豆搵仔咪起左幾隻香港人囉<br />\n想點"},{"pid":"66363ca23d3020a457528d9e19d677ad16b8734a","tid":1537812,"uid":262737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4c1caa5383a0513af04e1ddaf0fdd88acd18a499","tid":1537812,"uid":31151,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:23:23.000Z","msg":"鄧竟成個仔咪速龍 同市民互屌得最多就係佢地 點會係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:47:31.000Z","msg":"正解<br />\nd香港話唔知幾正宗"},{"pid":"de77b62ed510cf229e2ce64